k?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY5R%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=f251f25a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"749e0bd9554cbb44a67722bdec25e6bc4969a931","tid":2035213,"uid":304769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"626e18d339438cf629c76852ff5e298baffbda90","tid":2035213,"uid":4564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T18:50:41.000Z","msg":"功利d咁睇，BNO holders要有影響力一定係入tory, BoJo都係9萬幾黨員票就贏黨魁，labour要20幾萬票<br />\n<br />\nLibDem...唔會做到執政黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:37:48.000Z","msg":"好難咁樣講，libdem前身whig就係300年前第一個執政黨"},{"pid":"8d998f07bf0eecd5ed9d1fde0485d9db4a66869f","tid":2035213,"uid":4564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"749e0bd9554cbb44a67722bdec25e6bc4969a931","tid":2035213,"uid":304769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"626e18d339438cf629c76852ff5e298baffbda90","tid":2035213,"uid":4564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T18:50:41.000Z","msg":"功利d咁睇，BNO holders要有影響力一定係入tory, BoJo都係9萬幾黨員票就贏黨魁，labour要20幾萬票<br />\n<br />\nLibDem...唔會做到執政黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:37:48.000Z","msg":"好難咁樣講，libdem前身whig就係300年前第一個執政黨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:42:10.000Z","msg":"我知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上面已經講左功利d咁睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fe674ccbdf2c190d00968ce43c6f9ffed0a4b7e","tid":2035213,"uid":59773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T03:13:08.000Z","